OL,5, A former P&O Ferries chef is suing the 
OL,6, company and its chief executive,       
OL,7, claiming unfair dismissal, racial      
OL,8, discrimination and harassment.         
OL,10,FJohn Lansdown is the only seafarer to  
OL,11,Ftake legal action after 800 staff were 
OL,12,Fsacked without notice last month.      
OL,14,FIn his tribunal claim he accuses P&O of
OL,15,Ftreating him unfavourably as he is     
OL,16,FBritish and eligible for minimum wage. 
OL,18,FP&O Ferries said job cuts were         
OL,19,F"categorically not based on race or the
OL,20,Fnationality of the staff involved."    
